that you threw out there.

00:41:24,136 --> 00:41:26,206
You're gonna lose
both deals in a second.

00:41:26,206 --> 00:41:29,016
Lori, we came here wanting
to be partners with you.

00:41:29,016 --> 00:41:30,136
There's no question

00:41:30,136 --> 00:41:33,336
you are gonna bring
this product to America.

00:41:33,336 --> 00:41:35,356
One last shot--Will you
consider 20%,

00:41:35,356 --> 00:41:37,056
same deal,
and we have a deal?

00:41:38,866 --> 00:41:41,866
We buy back half,
20%, $200,000.

00:41:41,866 --> 00:41:43,166
What--

00:41:43,166 --> 00:41:44,236
No.

00:41:44,236 --> 00:41:47,986
Okay. 25% is your deal?

00:41:49,306 --> 00:41:51,206
You got a deal, Lori.
Great.

00:41:51,206 --> 00:41:54,086
Whoo!
All right.

00:41:54,086 --> 00:41:56,186
This is gonna be great.
We're very excited
to be partners.

00:41:56,186 --> 00:41:57,906
I gotta tell you,
I did not see that

00:41:57,906 --> 00:42:00,216
ending up the way it did.

00:42:00,216 --> 00:42:03,016
Congratulations.
Thanks so much.

00:42:03,016 --> 00:42:05,016
You got hustled, Lori.

00:42:05,016 --> 00:42:06,186
(laughs) I did not get hustled.

00:42:06,186 --> 00:42:07,186
The buyback...
is bad.

00:42:07,186 --> 00:42:08,316
The buyback was ridiculous.

00:42:08,316 --> 00:42:10,006
No. She didn't agree
to the buyback.

00:42:10,006 --> 00:42:11,116
Yes, she did.
You agreed
to the buyback?

00:42:11,116 --> 00:42:13,056
Four times. Four times.

00:42:13,056 --> 00:42:15,316
Lori, he out-sharked you
on that one.
That's his company--

00:42:15,316 --> 00:42:17,136
No, he didn't.
That's his company,

00:42:17,136 --> 00:42:20,286
and he has the right to have
the major stake in it.

00:42:20,286 --> 00:42:22,316
After you've taken
all the risk?
It--It--

00:42:22,316 --> 00:42:25,006
Help make us popular,
and then get out of here?
You guys, this is the decision

00:42:25,006 --> 00:42:27,136
that I made.
I made it for my reasons,

00:42:27,136 --> 00:42:29,186
and I think
it was the right decision.

00:42:29,186 --> 00:42:30,316
You cost us a fortune.
I did what
I thought was right,

00:42:30,316 --> 00:42:33,216
and--And I feel good about it.

00:42:33,216 --> 00:42:34,306
Whew!

